<opener><salute>Viro Clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi> et toto Orbe Celeberrimo
            <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Johanni Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs></salute></opener>
<p>Si vitam meam pro Te profunderem nullam partem vide<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rer tuorum meritorum assecutus Vir Doctissime. Tanta enim huma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nitate et quidem in tanta <choice><abbr>gravissimor.</abbr><expan>gravissimorum</expan></choice> negotiorum tuorum
             <lb/>multitudine responsum dare dignatus es non solum ad id quod
             <lb/>respicit <rs key="B_1715-01-25_991170515019005501" type="letter">negotialem meam epistolam</rs><note type="editorial">Michelotti an Johann I Bernoulli, 25. Januar 1715</note> verum etiam ad proble<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mata mechanico-medica doctrinam secretionis animalis spec<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tantia. De tua ad nos migratione desperassem penitus novis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sim<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> tua perlecta <rs key="B_1715-02-20_991170515018905501" type="letter">epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Johann I Bernoulli an Pietro Antonio Michelotti, 20. Februar 1715</note> nisi spem aliquam fecisset
             <lb/><choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzerus</rs> Tui amicissimus; cui <rs key="B_1715-02-20_991170515018905501" type="letter">tuas Litteras</rs> dedi, ipsique
             <lb/>uti et duobus reliquis tuis discipulis<note type="editorial">In seinem <rs key="B_1715-02-20_991170515018905501" type="letter">Brief</rs> vom 20. Februar 1715 berichtet Bernoulli, dass Johannes Scheuchzer mit zwei Freunden, die ebenfalls beide Mediziner waren, aus Neugierde nach Italien aufgebrochen sei.</note> valde doctis obtuli memet<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ipsum in omnibus iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ipsorum utilitati, aut curiositati
             <lb/>inservire possunt. Ipse <choice><abbr>Doctiss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Doctissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzerus</rs> (qui cum suis
             <lb/>sociis cras hinc <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavium</rs> discedet illinc post paucos dies
             <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3169070" type="place">Romam</rs> iturus) mihi dixit se avide expectare res<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ponsionem tuam ad <rs key="B_1715-02-16_991170515084705501" type="letter">postremam epistolam</rs> quam ad
             <lb/>Te misit: mihique facultatem impertivit <rs key="B_1715-03-27_991170515093405501" type="letter">Litteras respon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sorias</rs> aperiendi atque legendi; siquidem rogavit ut easdem
             <lb/>ad me transmitteres, quod semper efficere poteris. Sperat
             <lb/>idem <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimus</expan></choice> Vir Te tandem permotum iri non quidem
             <lb/>tantum ob honorificas adeo vocationes Professorum Pata<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vinorum nemini antehac factas ab hac <choice><abbr>Sereniss.<hi rend="sup">a</hi></abbr><expan>Serenissima</expan></choice> et
             <lb/>Potentissima <rs key="place_VER-repven" type="place">Republica</rs> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>m propter oblationem,
             <lb/>quam idem D. <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzerus</rs> Tibi fecit tecum permanen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>di <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs>. Spe itaque <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzeri</rs> fretus distuli
             <lb/>novissimas tuas litteras Amplissimo Moderatori <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410" type="person">Ruzzino</rs>
<pb facs="1078748" n="1v"/>
<lb/>ostendere: aususque sum etiam pro hac vice rogare ut patiaris
             <lb/>Te honorifice non quidem instar Mercenarii sed Princi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pis Mathematicorum adinstar conduci. Salarium initio propositum mehercule idem fuit ac illud quod nunc offer<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tur. <choice><orig><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></orig><reg><choice><orig><g ref="#AE">Æ</g></orig><reg>Ae</reg></choice></reg></choice>quivocatio contigit de Thaleris imperialibus: nunquam
             <lb/>enim Thaleros mille quinquecentum argenti unciis <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qui<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>valentes obtulerunt <choice><abbr>Illustr.</abbr><expan>Illustrissimi</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Excell.</abbr><expan>Excellissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatores</rs> nisi pro
             <lb/>argenti uncia Ducatus venetus intelligatur: Mille quinquecen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum floreni veneti fere <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quivalent 2250 florenis bel<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gicis aut germanicis. <choice><orig>etenim</orig><reg>Etenim</reg></choice> florenus venetus, ut intelliges
             <lb/>etiam a D. <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzero</rs>, proportionem habet fere sesquial<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>teram ad florenum belgicum aut germanicum. Ceterum
             <lb/>scias velim me acturum esse omnia diligenter ut etiam
             <lb/><choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzerus</rs> obtineat <choice><abbr>Med.<hi rend="sup">n<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></hi></abbr><expan>Medicin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></expan></choice> Theoric<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
             <lb/>propediem vacua erit: meque Tui amantissimum, et
             <lb/>erga Te gratissimum, fideque futurum fore conspicu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>.
             <lb/>A me nullum tempus praetermittetur de tuis rebus agendis et
             <lb/>cogitandis. De tua dignitate, et securitate; de tuo honore atque
             <lb/>summa existimatione tantum habeo polliceri me Tibi
             <lb/>cumulate Satisfacturum. Tu solus Vir summi nominis
             <lb/>excutere poteris pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>iudicium, quo contra <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatum</rs> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
             <lb/><choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimum</expan></choice> Nostrates laborant, eundemque in <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavina</rs>
<lb/><rs type="organisation">Cathedra</rs> collocare per tuum adventum valebis.</p> <closer><salute>Cur<unclear>a</unclear>
<lb/>ut valeas meque amare non desinas.</salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs>
<lb/><date when="1715-03-08">Octavo Idus Martii MDCCXV</date>.</dateline></closer>
<pb facs="1078749" n="2r"/>
<postscript><p>P. S.</p>
<p>Gratias Tibi ago maximas iterum atque iterum quod
         <lb/>aliquot eximiorum operum tuorum exemplaribus
         <lb/>me cumulare volueris; quodque dedignatus non fueris
         <lb/>mihi tradere solutionem problematis mechanico<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>medici a me propositi pro secretionis animalis doc<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>trina perficienda. Plura haberem hac super re dicenda
         <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ob temporis angustiam in proximam differo hebdo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>madam. Interim salutem plurimam mitto Doctissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mo Agnato tuo <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao</rs>; qui, ut spero, brevi nisi acceperit,
         <lb/>meas accipiet <rs key="B_1715-02-28_991170517052305501" type="letter">novissimas litteras</rs>.</p></postscript>
